cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision techniques for detecting and localizing road curbs using a monocular camera mounted on a vehicle. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories. The paper also deals with robotics and autonomous vehicles, which makes cs.RO (Robotics) a likely category. Finally, the paper involves the use of advanced vision-based detection methods, which makes cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category.
